{"tid":354953,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得打啲抵打既仆街係應該唔洗受到懲罰","createTime":"2017-08-11T01:46:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-13T04:46:12.000Z","uid":129942,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"17b60a4057d54fd1346593cea9a44b2a6c5bb0ee","tid":354953,"uid":129942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T01:46:22.000Z","msg":"好多時日常生活中會遇到好多好撚黑人憎既人<br />\n<br />\n例如喺戲院睇戲講野大大聲吵撚住人睇戲既人<br />\n<br />\n示意叫佢靜少少但佢個樣係話比你知<span style=\"color: red;\">我<br />\n<br />\n咁做有乜問題呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>既時候 其實真係好<br />\n<br />\n撚想捉佢出戲院門口然後打獲佢 <br />\n<br />\n又例如喺條好多人好逼既街上<br />\n<br />\n兩個人唔小心有少少碰撞<br />\n<br />\n你有禮貌地主動同佢講翻聲唔好意思既時候 <br />\n<br />\n明明可能唔關你事<br />\n<br />\n佢仲要西口西面對佢你再嘴渺渺啤住你搞到好似係你唔啱既時候<br />\n<br />\n又係想打獲佢<br />\n<br />\n奈何香港有法律令打人就會受到懲罰 嚴重既仲可能要留案底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n令好撚多仆街可以大搖大擺咁喺社會為非作歹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n覺得只要我地唔要面就做乜都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n反正你又唔可以郁我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無巴打同我有同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多時喺街到見到啲仆街但又乜都做唔到真係好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家點睇"},{"pid":"7f272f82af6eaee7648b68a5458a31cb198b3eac","tid":354953,"uid":48796,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T01:56:25.000Z","msg":"我覺得應該立法打鳩火車頭唔構成刑事罪行"},{"pid":"ce619c3b745789cf4743836aa76825973d70a40a","tid":354953,"uid":32439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T01:59:08.000Z","msg":"連登仔係現實咪又係唔敢出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67677841ee087631e509a5ea701da0cd89ade3c1","tid":354953,"uid":81505,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T02:00:30.000Z","msg":"好懷念中學打鳩d仆街<br />\n都剩係記過既日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個時有個仆街同學踢波落收山腳<br />\n直接一拳打落佢個鼻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"873a0c42c24c7202c13aaeabc4d304e2bb398ca8","tid":354953,"uid":73247,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T02:03:08.000Z","msg":"收皮啦，唔好講打，現實中勁多連聲都唔敢出，畀你合法打人又如何？"},{"pid":"d86cd7882344a7fc205bb90badc509cef7fb17db","tid":354953,"uid":48796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T06:36:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>收皮啦，唔好講打，現實中勁多連聲都唔敢出，畀你合法打人又如何？</blockquote><br />\n可能我敢出手唔敢出聲呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac084293e3f59806f0cd30b7f69b2c23a6c1bcea","tid":354953,"uid":59192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T06:44:11.000Z","msg":"咩叫仆街<br />\n點定義佢係仆街<br />\n暴力可以解決問題既話唔洗要法律啦"},{"pid":"d60664099649a47da514f6f6198d07296549fde7","tid":354953,"uid":129942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T07:30:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登仔係現實咪又係唔敢出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係唔敢出聲<br />\n因為我驚比人拍片擺上連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要打點會唔夠打"},{"pid":"968bb78e1c5d00b7e5fd04fe33f7f13bbd1a2e2b","tid":354953,"uid":129942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T07:32:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩叫仆街<br />\n點定義佢係仆街<br />\n暴力可以解決問題既話唔洗要法律啦</blockquote><br />\n法律可以解決問題咩？<br />\n淨係我個例子喺戲院大聲講野你已經奈佢唔何啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n叫職員？唔係對個個都有用<br />\n有啲人厚面皮賴死唔安靜你有乜計？"},{"pid":"e5d28904c41b79f2fa0aceb589a89b430b3a81fb","tid":354953,"uid":129942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T07:34:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>收皮啦，唔好講打，現實中勁多連聲都唔敢出，畀你合法打人又如何？</blockquote><br />\n可能我敢出手唔敢出聲呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個啱呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好以為個個連登仔都同你自己一樣咁潺先得㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b3c5c5f3047a249bce62130288415986f0f5a2b","tid":354953,"uid":73247,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T12:16:52.000Z","msg":"UCCU，網上講到幾兇狠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n現實大把打交啦，好少見到人出手幫，<br />\n個個都走先，費事上身，<br />\n香港人畀大陸人/南亞仔打果陣幾多人出手啫？"},{"pid":"f7810fe13aecb52a1ecd6c773c46040171090a85","tid":354953,"uid":60622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T12:32:32.000Z","msg":"屌你 打人打到表面無傷痕都唔識<br />\n<br />\n你慌班港豬比人打完會有錢驗身咩 唔使供樓呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acc3a4f98923590f10753a6eb878a9e17971b546","tid":354953,"uid":28767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T12:40:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩叫仆街<br />\n點定義佢係仆街<br />\n暴力可以解決問題既話唔洗要法律啦</blockquote><br />\n問題係法律好多問題都解決唔到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n戲院 排隊打尖呢啲已經係好例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70dfacf89b57d46f45a73dfc5071ddb1508257e1","tid":354953,"uid":60622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T04:46:12.000Z","msg":"根本打人就唔應該係犯法"}]}